---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="IR35 Contract Review Toolkit — £19 | Landolio">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">IR35 Contract Review Toolkit</h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-6">Everything you need to stay outside IR35 — contracts, clauses, checklists, and HMRC response templates</p>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">£19</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 line-through text-xl">£49</span>
        <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Limited Time</span>
      </div>
      <a href="#buy-now" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-xl transition shadow-lg">
        Download Now — £19 →
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Instant download · PDF format · No subscription</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Social Proof -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">✅ Used by <strong>200+ UK contractors</strong> to protect their IR35 status</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: February 2026 (includes latest HMRC guidance)</p>
    </div>

    <!-- What's Inside -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What's Inside</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-blue-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">📄 IR35-Proof Contract Template</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Ready-to-use contractor services agreement with all the right clauses:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Unlimited right of substitution (HMRC-compliant wording)</li>
            <li>Client control limitations (autonomy over methods)</li>
            <li>Fixed-term project structure (avoids MOO)</li>
            <li>Equipment and financial risk provisions</li>
            <li>Editable in Word/Google Docs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-green-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">📋 Substitution Clause Library</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">10+ pre-written substitution clauses for different situations:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Unlimited substitution (strongest)</li>
            <li>Limited substitution (for sensitive work)</li>
            <li>Technical specialist substitution</li>
            <li>Agency-mediated substitution</li>
            <li>Copy-paste into your contracts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-purple-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">✅ Evidence-Gathering Checklist</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Protect yourself from HMRC challenges:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>What documents to save (contracts, emails, invoices)</li>
            <li>How to prove substitution rights</li>
            <li>Evidence of multiple clients</li>
            <li>Working practice documentation</li>
            <li>CEST result storage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-red-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">📧 HMRC Challenge Response Templates</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Ready-to-send letters if HMRC challenges your status:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Initial enquiry response</li>
            <li>Evidence submission letter</li>
            <li>Disagreement with determination</li>
            <li>Appeal request template</li>
            <li>Professional advisor engagement letter</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🎯 IR35 Self-Assessment Scorecard</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Score your contracts before you sign:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>25-point IR35 risk assessment</li>
            <li>Red flags checklist</li>
            <li>Contract negotiation tips</li>
            <li>When to walk away</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-indigo-500">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">📊 BONUS: IR35 Financial Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">See the real cost of inside vs outside IR35:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Take-home income comparison</li>
            <li>Tax savings from dividends</li>
            <li>Break-even analysis</li>
            <li>Excel spreadsheet (editable)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Who This Is For -->
    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who This Is For</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">✅ Perfect if you:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li>✓ Work through a limited company (PSC)</li>
            <li>✓ Want to stay outside IR35</li>
            <li>✓ Need IR35-compliant contract templates</li>
            <li>✓ Are negotiating a new contract</li>
            <li>✓ Want to challenge a client's inside IR35 determination</li>
            <li>✓ Need evidence for HMRC</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">❌ Not suitable if:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li>✗ You're a sole trader (not a PSC)</li>
            <li>✗ You're an employee (PAYE)</li>
            <li>✗ You work through an umbrella company</li>
            <li>✗ You're happy inside IR35</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Problem -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Problem</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        IR35 is costing UK contractors <strong>20-30% of their income</strong> — and most don't even know they're at risk until HMRC sends a tax demand.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500 mb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Common Mistakes That Get Contractors Caught:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <li>❌ Signing contracts with "personal service" clauses (no substitution)</li>
          <li>❌ Working from the client's office full-time (fails control test)</li>
          <li>❌ Staying with one client for 12+ months (fails MOO test)</li>
          <li>❌ Not keeping evidence of working practices</li>
          <li>❌ Accepting inside IR35 determinations without challenge</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        <strong>The cost of getting IR35 wrong:</strong> A contractor earning £60,000 outside IR35 takes home £45,000. The same person inside IR35 takes home just £36,000 — a <strong>£9,000 annual loss</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The Solution -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Solution</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        This toolkit gives you everything you need to:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Protect Your Status</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Use IR35-proof contracts with all the right clauses</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">📋</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Gather Evidence</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Build a defensible position if HMRC challenges you</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">✉️</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Respond to HMRC</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Ready-to-send templates if you're challenged</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials (Placeholder) -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What Contractors Say</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-4 border-blue-500">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">"This toolkit saved me £12,000 a year. I was about to accept an inside IR35 contract, but after using the contract template and negotiating better terms, the client agreed I was outside IR35."</p>
          <p class="font-semibold">— Sarah M., IT Contractor</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-t-4 border-green-500">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">"The HMRC challenge response templates were invaluable. HMRC questioned my status, and I used the evidence checklist and response letter to defend my position. They accepted it."</p>
          <p class="font-semibold">— James T., Finance Contractor</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Buy Now Section -->
    <div id="buy-now" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 text-white p-12 rounded-lg text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Get the IR35 Contract Review Toolkit</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-6">Protect your status. Keep your income. Stay outside IR35.</p>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <span class="text-5xl font-bold">£19</span>
        <span class="text-xl line-through ml-3 opacity-75">£49</span>
      </div>
      <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK_PLACEHOLDER" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-xl transition shadow-lg">
        Download Now — £19 →
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm mt-4 opacity-90">Instant download · Secure payment via Stripe · PDF format · No subscription</p>
      <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-blue-500">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">What You Get:</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 max-w-md mx-auto text-left">
          <li>✓ IR35-proof contract template (Word/PDF)</li>
          <li>✓ Substitution clause library (10+ clauses)</li>
          <li>✓ Evidence-gathering checklist</li>
          <li>✓ HMRC challenge response templates (5 letters)</li>
          <li>✓ IR35 self-assessment scorecard</li>
          <li>✓ BONUS: Financial calculator (Excel)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQs -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Is this better than HMRC's CEST tool?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">No — this toolkit <strong>complements</strong> CEST. CEST tells you your status; this toolkit helps you <strong>stay outside IR35</strong> by giving you contract templates and evidence-gathering tools. Use both.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I use this for existing contracts?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Yes — use the substitution clauses and negotiation tips to renegotiate your current contract, or prepare better for your next one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Is this legal advice?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">No — this is educational content and templates. It is not a substitute for professional legal or tax advice. For complex or high-value contracts, consult an IR35 specialist.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What format is the toolkit?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">PDF (for guides and checklists) + Word/Google Docs (for contract templates) + Excel (for calculator). All editable and ready to use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Do I get updates?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Yes — we update this toolkit when IR35 rules change. If you buy now, you'll get free updates for 12 months (email delivery).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What if it doesn't help?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">If you're not satisfied, email us within 30 days for a full refund. No questions asked.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Don't Lose 20-30% of Your Income to IR35</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Get the tools you need to stay outside IR35 and protect your take-home pay.</p>
      <a href="#buy-now" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-xl transition shadow-lg">
        Download IR35 Contract Review Toolkit — £19 →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
